{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throttleConfigure","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"interval"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int32","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"acceleration","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int32","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"deceleration"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int32","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unreliable packets are dropped by ENet in response to the varying conditions of the Internet connection to the peer. The throttle represents a probability that an unreliable packet should not be dropped and thus sent by ENet to the peer. By measuring fluctuations in round trip times of reliable packets over the specified "},{"code":"interval","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", ENet will either increase the probability by the amount specified in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"acceleration"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter, or decrease it by the amount specified in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"deceleration"},{"text":" parameter (both are ratios to ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/packetThrottleScale","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the throttle has a value of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/packetThrottleScale","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", no unreliable packets are dropped by ENet, and so 100% of all unreliable packets will be sent.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the throttle has a value of ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", all unreliable packets are dropped by ENet, and so 0% of all unreliable packets will be sent."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Intermediate values for the throttle represent intermediate probabilities between 0% and 100% of unreliable packets being sent. The bandwidth limits of the local and foreign hosts are taken into account to determine a sensible limit for the throttle probability above which it should not raise even in the best of conditions."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/enetpacketpeer\/throttleconfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Configures throttle parameter for a peer."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot14ENetPacketPeerC17throttleConfigure8interval12acceleration12decelerationys5Int32V_A2ItF","title":"throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"throttleConfigure"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"interval"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V","text":"Int32","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"acceleration","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V","text":"Int32"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"deceleration","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int32","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/ENetPacketPeer":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/enetpacketpeer","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ENetPacketPeer","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A wrapper class for an [url=http:\/\/enet.bespin.org\/group__peer.html]ENetPeer[\/url]."}],"title":"ENetPacketPeer","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ENetPacketPeer"}]},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/ENetPacketPeer/throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"throttleConfigure","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"interval","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V","text":"Int32","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"acceleration","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int32","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"deceleration"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int32V","text":"Int32","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Configures throttle parameter for a peer.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/enetpacketpeer\/throttleconfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)","role":"symbol","title":"throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot","title":"SwiftGodot","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Framework to write Godot Game Extensions using the Swift Programming Language."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/ENetPacketPeer/packetThrottleScale":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"packetThrottleScale"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"packetThrottleScale","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The reference value for throttle configuration. The default value is "},{"code":"32","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". See ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/throttleConfigure(interval:acceleration:deceleration:)","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/ENetPacketPeer\/packetThrottleScale","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/enetpacketpeer\/packetthrottlescale","role":"symbol"}}}